sentences: His first single, "The Tropics", was  released in 2013.
The track reached No. 14 on the Australian ARIA Charts and No. 22 on Triple J Hottest 100, 2015, and was nominated for a 2016 ARIA Award for Best Dance Release and for Breakthrough Artist.
Carmody was previously a member of Carmada alongside Max Armata.
He left the duo in 2018 to focus on his solo career.
